  "text": "Experimental diets were consisted of 30% fat and 25% sucrose on a calorie basis. The composition of the diets was based on the AIN-93G [CITATION_1] with modifications as described previously [CITATION_2] . Beef tallow or fish oil was used in the diets instead of soybean oil (B diet or F diet, Table 1) .",
